**  CMT1/CMT2 (COMMENT NAME)
0 CANCEL                                                   1
1 UPDATED                                                  2
2 ADD                                                      3
3 SET NBR                                                  4
4 K KIND                                                   5
5 CHOP_D                                                   6
6 EFF DATE                                                 7
7 LAPSE_D                                                  8
